scene.message:
Mark: Tch!{nl}
It was a trap after all!{nl}
{ctl0f:1}, let's go!{waitkey}{ret}

Hariti: Maki...?{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Maki, I finally found you.{nl}
You're safe...{waitkey}{ret}

Hariti: Mother has been{nl}
searching for you, Maki...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
Come {wait_fr:21}Maki, {wait_fr:21}to Mother...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Maki!{wait_fr:16}{nl}
No good - she seems to be{nl}
controlled by that Demon...{waitkey}{clearbox}The voice does sound like{nl}
Maki's mother{wait_fr:32}, but{nl}
we can't trust it!{waitkey}{clearbox}{ctl07:1}, let's fight!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey, are you sure{nl}
about this, {ctl0f:1}?!{waitkey}{clearbox}Sonomura might get killed{nl}
by that monster!{nl}
Let's take it down quick!{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: You okay leaving{nl}
Sonomura like that, {ctl0f:1}?{nl}
We gotta beat that demon!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: But that voice...{nl}
It's gotta be Sonomura's{nl}
mom's voice, right?{waitkey}{clearbox}I dunno why she's dressed{nl}
like that, but what if it's{nl}
really her mom...?{waitkey}{ctl0f:1}, we can't fight her!{waitkey}{ret}

Hariti: Why do you{nl}
stand in my way...?{nl}
Give back my daughter!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: Oh...{wait_fr:32} where{wait_fr:32}{nl}
am I... isn't this the{nl}
infirmary?{waitkey}{clearbox}My, it's a haunted house.{nl}
I was just dreaming of{nl}
that very thing.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: In this world,{nl}
Sonomura's mom{nl}
doesn't exist...{waitkey}{clearbox}...She's the real deal!{nl}
But why is she here...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Ma'am, are you okay?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: Yes,{nl}
I'm fine...{waitkey}When Maki was little, she'd{nl}
get lost in the haunted{nl}
house, and I'd find her.{waitkey}{clearbox}As I searched this vast{nl}
mansion all alone,{nl}
I heard Maki calling...{waitkey}After that, I don't{nl}
remember a thing.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Listen, ma'am...{nl}
I'm really not{nl}
your child.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: I see...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
You're the Maki of{nl}
this world.{waitkey}{clearbox}But why is there no me{nl}
in this world, I wonder...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: This passage{nl}
is very unstable.{waitkey}{clearbox}Someone must stay here{nl}
and operate the machine.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Someone has to{nl}
stay behind?{nl}
No - I won't leave anyone!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: I'll do it!{nl}
I'll keep the passage{nl}
stable, so don't worry - go.{waitkey}{clearbox}Though... it would make me{nl}
happy if you came back{nl}
for me once it's all over.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I don't have{nl}
a mother, but...{waitkey}{clearbox}I wish I'd had a kind{nl}
mother like you{wait_fr:32},{nl}
I really do...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Once we beat Kandori,{nl}
I'll be sure to find your{nl}
"little Maki" too!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: ...{wait_fr:16}...{wait_fr:16}...{wait_fr:16}...{wait_fr:16}{nl}
Yes, that's right.{wait_fr:64}{nl}
Thank you...{waitkey}{ret}
